org.apache.calcite.sql

接口 SqlSpecialOperator.TokenSequence

  • 封闭类:
    SqlSpecialOperator

    public static interface SqlSpecialOperator.TokenSequence
    List of tokens: the input to a parser. Every token is either an operator (SqlOperator) or an expression (SqlNode), and every token has a position.
